for unchecked parse behavior that no longer exists.\n  - Adjusted out-of-range parse assertion to match current `ParseException` behavior.\n\n- `TimestampsTest.java`\n  - Replaced removed `Timestamps.parseUnchecked` calls with supported `Timestamps.parse`.\n  - Removed tests for removed `Timestamps.fromDate` and `Timestamps.now`.\n  - Cast `Timestamps.NANOS_PER_SECOND` where the current API expects `int nanos`.\n  - Adjusted parse exception cause assertion to match current behavior.\n\nI did not run Gradle/tests, per instruction. Also noted there was already a modified `metadata/com.google.protobuf/protobuf-java-util/index.json`; I left it untouched.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_029acd7297ef679a016a24e2af21f88194a45843ac8b7809b6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 593, "output": 1219, "cacheRead": 80384, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 82196, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "error", "timestamp": 1780802201948, "responseId": "resp_029acd7297ef679a016a24e29b72ec81948165e3c009fb172c", "errorMessage": "terminated"}}
